"'''Dark Eyes, Warm Thoughts'''" was a [[dusk]] song written by [[Erik Lauderslag]], performed by [[Far Cry]] on [[Tuttin IV]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Beneath the bassline was a message embedded by [[Ryley Ancum]] to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] concerning an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] shipment of metals for a new warship.<ref name="GC6">{{GamerCite|6|Rebel Bass}}</ref>

